LibreAssist - AI-powered Agentic Writing for LibreOffice

LibreAssist is a LibreOffice extension that brings agentic AI writing assistance directly into your documents. Instead of a simple chat interface, the AI works directly on your files.

Features:
- Agentic document editing via Claude Code CLI, Codex CLI and Mistral Vibe CLI
- Session-aware chat with persistent conversation history
- Undo/Redo for AI changes
- Custom instructions for every request
- Configurable provider setup via providers.json
- Multi-language support (English, German, French, Italian, Spanish)

Requires a paid API key or access for Claude, OpenAI Code or Mistral.
